blockquote><blockquote>[<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自從 副學士依個 on 9 level 出現之後 <br />\n<br />\ndiploma 不如同 high diploma 合併算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句,  bba (只要係香港認可機構既) 點都好過 high dip , diploma 啦<br />\n尤其係坐 office 既工 <br />\n<br />\n如果係技術型既工,  high diploma 都仲有存在價值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5276c2781db02fc7e50457506a2d1b840553c628","tid":258231,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299bdd0bd2aa5509366345d72e07dab9ddd17d2f","tid":258231,"uid":1024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n搭單一問<br />\n但BBA 都有分好多科<br />\n其實係咪應該跟興趣簡？<br />\n但對呢啲咩都唔識 應該點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHd 畢業<br />\noffice ps 都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家都做緊啲好煩 好悶 但又唔簡單 既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩先開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊Contract 工 係咪唔會教你咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身諗住我都係求其搵啲野做住先 諗住hea下咁做<br />\n點知咁多野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇左呢個post 先知admin有得升職有得讀<br />\n咁我都可能會諗下會唔會讀返pt degree <br />\n唔該哂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70390b1d46e6c5b4b36218eff19922517215a474","tid":258231,"uid":12494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Fg 去左某上市大公司做admin 5年<br />\n打雜之餘跟一個gm <br />\n跟住轉executive assistant-》sec <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲 ?<br />\n<br />\n大公司 secretary ,  有前途呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家做唔返細公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0fc42e44b522b0c4f3beec2ea63f8130f5b437","tid":258231,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中五仔 做左幾年office admin <br />\n而家 15k 讀緊 pt bba<br />\n老細話讀完比我升officer 我諗都係20k 倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打老細真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講多d pt bba既嘢？<br />\n要比幾多學費 <br />\n我依家google下資料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0fc246f7ba1280c18d5dcf1a030722db668525","tid":258231,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fac16070cb047ce4252762e6d2056c5567edcb","tid":258231,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2df3211ab31a6